============================================================================
This is an adoptable module. The original maintainer has told the PAUSE 
admins they he's making these modules available for immediate transfer
to a future maintainer. Write to modules@perl.org to get maintainership
of this module.
============================================================================

You can install this using in the usual Perl fashion

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install
        
The documentation is in the module file.  Once you install
the file, you can read it with perldoc.

	perldoc Text::MacroScript 
        
If you want to read it before you install it, you can use
perldoc directly on the module file.

	perldoc MacroScript.pm
        
This module is also in Github

	https://github.com/briandfoy/Text-MacroScript


Enjoy, 

brian d foy, bdfoy@cpan.org
